            "heading": "Technical specifications",
            "text": "<p><strong>TREATMENT TIME: </strong>3 minutes</p><p><strong>CERTIFICATES: </strong>FDA, TGA, CE, UKCA</p><p><strong>OPERATION: </strong>Wireless, hands-free</p><p><strong>WAVELENGTH: </strong>415nm (Blue), 605nm (Amber), 630nm (Red), 660nm (Deep Red), 880nm (Infrared)</p><p><strong>TREATMENT TIME: </strong>2 hours</p><p><strong>CHARGING TIME: </strong>3 minutes</p><p><strong>LEDs: </strong>160 dual core</p>"
