          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Treatment details",
            "text": "<p><strong>USE: </strong>Use daily after cleansing, before topical skincare</p><p><strong>SKIN REJUVENATING TREATMENT: </strong>415nm (Blue), 605nm (Amber), 630nm (Red), 660nm (Deep Red), 880nm (Infrared)</p><p><strong>SKIN CLEARING TREATMENT: </strong>415nm (Blue), 630nm (Red)</p><p><strong>CUSTOMIZED TREATMENT: </strong>Choose treatment modes for each facial area via app</p><p><strong>Skin Type: </strong>Most suitable for Fitzpatrick Skin Types I-IV</p>"
