      "name": "t:sections.how-it-works.name",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "How it works",
        "text": "<p>The Q-Rejuvalight Pro LED mask uses 5 light wavelengths and two modes for customizable skincare. Our FDA-cleared device targets your skin's needs.</p>",
        "image_aging": "shopify://shop_images/mask_aging.webp",
        "image_breakout": "shopify://shop_images/mask_breakout.webp",
        "heading_aging_mode": "<p><strong>Skin Rejuvenating</strong></p>",
        "text_aging_mode": "<p>On Skin Rejuvenating, red and infrared wavelengths work together to help support collagen production, which reduces the appearance of wrinkles and fine lines, as well as to improve skin elasticity and firmness.</p><p>Red light stimulates collagen and elastin production, which supports skin renewal. Deep red light penetrates deeper to help with the appearance of wrinkles, while infrared is designed to reach deeper layers for potential long-term benefits.</p>",
        "heading_breakout_mode": "<p><strong>Skin Clearing</strong></p>",
        "text_breakout_mode": "<p>Our Skin Clearing combines blue and red light wavelengths. Blue (415 nm) targets acne-causing bacteria on the skin's surface, and red (630 nm) helps calm inflammation and soothes irritated skin.</p><p>Together, these wavelengths help reduce breakouts, prevent future flare-ups, and support clearer, healthier-looking skin.</p>"
      }
    },
